&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for dynamic forward thinking Band 5 nurses to join our integrated award winning community nursing team, you will work alongside General practitioners, Physiotherapists, occupational therapists and external care agencies all caring for patients with long term conditions who require support with re-enablement, rehabilitation, and may have complex discharge requirements. D47 is based at City Hospital in the Sheldon block.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As Nurse and therapy led units the there is a strong commitment to support you from clinical team leaders, supervision and team work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like to be part of our forward thinking teams and support us in our trusts 2020 vision with regards to our ongoing work in striving for an outstanding CQC rating and you are innovative, have good communication skills and ready for a new challenge, then why not join our Nursing teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
